title: Herbs Dictionary Pro
description: Herbs Dictionary app is a comprehensive List of Medicinal Herbs and their amazing Uses with Pictures and Sounds. It is a complete guide to common medicinal herbs. When you began to look into traditional cuisines of various cultures there was a common thread in all of them – the use of herbs. Herbs are a great way to purify your mind and body. In this app you will find a complete list of herbs and how to use them to reduce stress, increase your energy, strength, stamina, memory and much more.
